1
00:01:03,880 --> 00:01:04,560
This is...

2
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:09,210
This is actually the nine-tailed phoenix pattern used by the Empress.

3
00:01:14,320 --> 00:01:15,240
You are crazy.

4
00:01:16,039 --> 00:01:19,970
How dare you tear up the marriage certificate approved by the Emperor!

5
00:01:20,080 --> 00:01:22,240
That young master of the Xie family is already blind.

6
00:01:22,240 --> 00:01:24,700
Are you still going to remain chaste for him?

7
00:01:25,039 --> 00:01:26,160
Now,

8
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:27,600
that vixen Yan Qingshu

9
00:01:27,600 --> 00:01:30,520
has climbed the social ladder and become an imperial concubine.

10
00:01:30,520 --> 00:01:32,840
Why can't you live up to expectations?

11
00:01:33,240 --> 00:01:35,100
Mother, there is no need to panic.

12
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:37,880
The imperial sedan chair must pass through seven gates.

13
00:01:37,880 --> 00:01:39,560
The nails on the Vermilion Bird Gate fall easily.

14
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:41,800
The covers of the Black Tortoise wells are slippery.

15
00:01:41,800 --> 00:01:43,400
Perhaps this bride

16
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:46,100
won't even make it past the third threshold.

17
00:01:47,080 --> 00:01:47,960
Do you

18
00:01:49,160 --> 00:01:50,320
have another plan?

19
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:51,640
As for my plan,

20
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:53,200
Mother,

21
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:56,720
haven't you already helped me?

22
00:02:27,160 --> 00:02:30,240
You asked me to disguise myself as a pastry chef at Vermilion Bird Tower

23
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:31,570
to poison her pastries.

24
00:02:31,640 --> 00:02:33,120
It's been a while.

25
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:36,360
But the poison hasn't taken effect yet.

26
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:39,079
By my calculation,

27
00:02:39,760 --> 00:02:41,480
it's about time for her.

28
00:02:45,760 --> 00:02:47,200
Defying a decree

29
00:02:47,200 --> 00:02:48,930
is a crime of great disrespect.

30
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,640
The Emperor is merciful.

31
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:53,760
He only orders you two to kneel here and reflect.

32
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:57,120
Be careful.

33
00:02:57,640 --> 00:02:58,440
Your Majesty.

34
00:02:59,040 --> 00:03:01,100
I would rather suffer any punishment

35
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:04,400
than marry Prince Ling's daughter.

36
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:06,360
Your Majesty.

37
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:08,520
I would rather become a nun

38
00:03:09,160 --> 00:03:11,090
than enter the palace as a consort.

39
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:22,400
Miss Yan.

40
00:03:22,880 --> 00:03:25,840
His Majesty summons you to the imperial study.

41
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:47,360
Your Majesty.

42
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:49,650
Yan Qingshu has been brought here.

43
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:52,560
I pay my respects to Your Majesty.

44
00:03:52,920 --> 00:03:53,920
Yan Qingshu.

45
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:55,720
I recently obtained an old item.

46
00:03:55,720 --> 00:03:56,850
Do you recognize it?

47
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:01,650
This is my father's peace pendant.

48
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:03,460
Where did Your Majesty get it?

49
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:07,160
I just learned of the Duke's whereabouts

50
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,560
and immediately summoned you to the palace.

51
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:09,720
How have I treated you?

52
00:04:09,720 --> 00:04:11,040
Where is my father now?

53
00:04:14,200 --> 00:04:15,720
Guiku City in the north.

54
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:19,360
The Duke suffers severe torture every day.

55
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:21,959
I'm afraid he won't last much longer.

56
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:30,320
Xiao Jingyan.

57
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:33,080
I will make you personally taste the bitterness

58
00:04:33,080 --> 00:04:36,040
of separation from loved ones, gathering with hated ones,

59
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:37,720
and unfulfilled desires.

60
00:04:50,320 --> 00:04:51,360
Xiao Jingyan.

61
00:04:52,159 --> 00:04:53,080
Is marrying me

62
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:55,360
so difficult for you?

63
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:56,659
Princess Linlang.

64
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:59,570
I am the one who killed your father.

65
00:05:01,520 --> 00:05:03,200
The winner becomes king, and the loser becomes the outlaw.

66
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:04,880
The world and empire you men fight for,

67
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:06,010
I don't understand.

68
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:08,650
I only need to marry my beloved.

69
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:11,880
This is the best destiny for a woman.

70
00:05:14,640 --> 00:05:16,040
Your Majesty summoned me

71
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:19,840
to make a deal with me.

72
00:05:20,520 --> 00:05:22,640
In exchange for my entering the palace as a concubine,

73
00:05:22,640 --> 00:05:25,280
Your Majesty will send troops to Beidi

74
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:27,120
to save my father.

75
00:05:29,280 --> 00:05:30,600
What a clever girl.

76
00:05:31,440 --> 00:05:32,280
Yan Qingshu,

77
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:34,360
you are indeed exceptionally courageous.

78
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:35,960
But you are also so audacious

79
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,640
as to defy an imperial decree.

80
00:05:37,640 --> 00:05:38,640
Believe it or not,

81
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:40,970
I can use trumped-up charges right now

82
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:42,520
to execute Xiao Jingyan.

83
00:05:42,520 --> 00:05:44,720
Your Majesty is so eager to silence him,

84
00:05:44,960 --> 00:05:47,400
fearing the Prince will uncover

85
00:05:47,440 --> 00:05:49,440
your unspeakable secrets.

86
00:05:52,840 --> 00:05:54,770
What unspeakable secret do I have?

87
00:05:57,200 --> 00:05:59,130
The mastermind behind Prince Ling

88
00:05:59,880 --> 00:06:01,410
is not the Empress Dowager.

89
00:06:05,280 --> 00:06:07,210
The mastermind behind Prince Ling

90
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,200
is the Empress Dowager.

91
00:06:09,200 --> 00:06:10,080
Perhaps it is.

92
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:12,040
Perhaps

93
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:16,440
it is someone more powerful than the Empress Dowager.

94
00:06:22,840 --> 00:06:24,570
The Duke cannot wait that long.

95
00:06:24,880 --> 00:06:26,340
Think about it carefully.

96
00:06:26,640 --> 00:06:28,560
Why does Your Majesty insist on marrying me?

97
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:30,520
I fell in love with you at first sight.

98
00:06:30,520 --> 00:06:31,600
Is this reason enough?

99
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:32,930
What Your Majesty said,

100
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:34,970
do you believe it yourself?

101
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:37,920
Whether I believe it or not is not important.

102
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:39,450
I will wait for your answer.

103
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,920
I will absolutely not marry you.

104
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:50,440
Why?

105
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:52,250
Because between you and me,

106
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:55,640
there is absolutely no romantic affection.

107
00:06:55,640 --> 00:06:57,040
I am a noble Princess.

108
00:06:57,840 --> 00:06:59,440
I am breathtakingly beautiful.

109
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:01,600
If you can't feel romantic affection for me,

110
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:02,920
that is your problem.

111
00:07:03,200 --> 00:07:04,760
What does it have to do with me?

112
00:07:04,760 --> 00:07:06,520
I already have someone I love.

113
00:07:06,640 --> 00:07:07,840
That doesn't matter.

114
00:07:07,840 --> 00:07:09,440
You just need to marry me.

115
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:24,640
Let's go.

116
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:30,040
Okay.

117
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:52,560
I'm going to Beidi to save my father.

118
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:54,050
You can't go.

119
00:07:54,159 --> 00:07:54,920
It's a trap.

120
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:57,400
How do you know it's a trap?

121
00:07:57,400 --> 00:07:57,880
I...

122
00:07:59,080 --> 00:08:00,960
Anyway, you have to believe me.

123
00:08:03,440 --> 00:08:04,600
You already knew

124
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:07,640
my father was trapped in Guiku City.

125
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:13,540
Stop the carriage.

126
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:16,020
Stop the carriage.

127
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:18,920
Qingshu, Qingshu.

128
00:08:19,320 --> 00:08:20,880
I have fought against this Wise Prince of the Right.

129
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:22,280
He has always been a liar.

130
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:23,200
If you go alone,

131
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:24,440
not only will you fail to save anyone,

132
00:08:24,440 --> 00:08:26,440
but you will also lose your own life.

133
00:08:26,960 --> 00:08:27,890
For this matter,

134
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:30,010
we need to think it over carefully.

135
00:08:30,960 --> 00:08:33,000
How do you know I haven't thought it over?

136
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:35,280
How do you know I don't have a thorough plan?

137
00:08:35,280 --> 00:08:35,919
Qingshu.

138
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:37,919
Let me go.

139
00:08:38,159 --> 00:08:38,559
Calm down.

140
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:39,440
Let me go.

141
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,610
Qingshu, calm down.

142
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:42,240
Let me.

143
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:52,240
Qingshu.

144
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:54,680
I'm sorry.

145
00:08:55,680 --> 00:08:56,920
I had no other choice.

146
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:15,370
I will definitely find a way

147
00:09:15,560 --> 00:09:16,720
to rescue the Duke.

148
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:28,920
Qingshu.

149
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:31,490
Words from Beidi

150
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:33,140
must never be trusted.

151
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:35,650
Especially that Right Prince.

152
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,360
That's exactly why

153
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:40,540
it needs to be verified in person.

154
00:09:43,280 --> 00:09:44,480
I need your help.

155
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:45,440
Okay.

156
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:48,250
Marrying Prince Ling's daughter,

157
00:09:49,880 --> 00:09:50,840
are you willing?

158
00:09:51,880 --> 00:09:54,120
You want me to marry my enemy's daughter?

159
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:54,760
Then you want to

160
00:09:54,760 --> 00:09:57,360
marry the Emperor and enter the palace as a concubine.

161
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:57,840
I forbid it.

162
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:59,370
It's an expedient measure.

163
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:03,640
Only by pretending to agree to the marriage

164
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:05,920
and making the Emperor lower his guard,

165
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:08,840
can we have a chance to go to Beidi

166
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:11,040
and find out the truth.

167
00:10:29,640 --> 00:10:30,280
Father.

168
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:33,200
Your unfilial son

169
00:10:34,280 --> 00:10:35,120
is late.

170
00:10:39,760 --> 00:10:40,560
Young Master.

171
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:41,680
Before he passed away, the master ordered me

172
00:10:41,680 --> 00:10:43,280
to give this letter to you.

173
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:53,560
You must not follow the path of your ancestors.

174
00:10:53,560 --> 00:10:55,090
It is a path to destruction.

175
00:10:55,800 --> 00:10:56,360
Yuheng,

176
00:10:57,120 --> 00:10:59,560
the Xie family has been officials for three generations,

177
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:01,360
with an impeccable reputation.

178
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:05,040
Condemned by everyone,

179
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:07,000
spat upon by all.

180
00:11:07,880 --> 00:11:09,920
I failed to teach you well.

181
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:11,840
I have shamed our ancestors.

182
00:11:12,880 --> 00:11:14,940
I shouldn't have served Prince Ling.

183
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:16,840
One wrong step

184
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:19,080
leads to a total loss.

185
00:11:20,280 --> 00:11:22,560
If you can revive the Xie family one day,

186
00:11:23,280 --> 00:11:24,800
even in the netherworld,

187
00:11:25,160 --> 00:11:26,560
I will rest in peace.

188
00:11:27,640 --> 00:11:28,480
Remember.

189
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:30,720
In the court,

190
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:33,280
power is the foundation of survival.

191
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:35,850
Only by constantly climbing up

192
00:11:36,560 --> 00:11:40,400
can you revive the Xie family.

193
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:46,760
Father.

194
00:11:48,520 --> 00:11:49,800
Rest in peace.

195
00:11:50,560 --> 00:11:52,000
I swear here

196
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:54,340
that I will revive the Xie family.

197
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:57,320
Even if I have to use any means necessary

198
00:11:57,800 --> 00:11:59,120
or sacrifice my life,

199
00:11:59,120 --> 00:12:00,760
I will not let you down.

200
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:06,010
Brother Yuheng.

201
00:12:06,520 --> 00:12:07,600
Let me help you

202
00:12:09,640 --> 00:12:10,900
revive the Xie family.

203
00:12:25,160 --> 00:12:26,840
You came home this late.

204
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:29,000
If people see you, they will gossip.

205
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:31,080
How can you marry a good family then?

206
00:12:32,040 --> 00:12:33,720
How much money do you still have?

207
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:34,680
Give it all to me.

208
00:12:35,160 --> 00:12:37,290
Why do you need so much money suddenly?

209
00:12:37,920 --> 00:12:38,600
Usually,

210
00:12:38,680 --> 00:12:40,720
you have never been short of money.

211
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:44,000
I need to help Yuheng with his official post.

212
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:45,720
Are you out of your mind?

213
00:12:45,800 --> 00:12:46,520
Why did I give birth to

214
00:12:46,520 --> 00:12:48,320
such a disappointing daughter?

215
00:12:48,680 --> 00:12:50,600
Losing money and ruining your reputation,

216
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:52,200
are you trying to make me mad?

217
00:12:53,400 --> 00:12:56,060
After all, he is the son of the Minister of Works.

218
00:12:56,280 --> 00:12:57,680
Now that he is in trouble,

219
00:12:57,760 --> 00:12:59,220
if I offer him timely help,

220
00:12:59,680 --> 00:13:02,000
when he revives his family's glory in the future,

221
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:03,160
he will surely not forget my kindness.

222
00:13:03,160 --> 00:13:05,220
When I marry into the Xie family then,

223
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:07,920
there's no doubt he will cherish me.

224
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:11,760
You still want to marry him?

225
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:14,440
Marrying a blind man?

226
00:13:15,760 --> 00:13:18,000
A blind man wanting to revive his family's glory

227
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:19,440
is simply a fool's dream.

228
00:13:19,760 --> 00:13:21,920
Yan Mingli, wake up.

229
00:13:22,920 --> 00:13:25,320
Xie Yuheng is cowardly and irresponsible.

230
00:13:25,440 --> 00:13:27,770
He lacks courage and has no mind of his own.

231
00:13:28,160 --> 00:13:29,760
Let alone being an official,

232
00:13:29,800 --> 00:13:32,480
he can't even take care of himself now.

233
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:34,560
He is also a wanted criminal.

234
00:13:35,160 --> 00:13:36,690
With such a useless person,

235
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:39,520
do you still expect him to rise rapidly in officialdom?

236
00:13:39,520 --> 00:13:41,040
Are you stupid?

237
00:13:45,640 --> 00:13:47,170
I have said all I have to say.

238
00:13:48,280 --> 00:13:50,200
If you remain so stubborn,

239
00:13:50,640 --> 00:13:51,440
in the future,

240
00:13:51,880 --> 00:13:55,010
you won't even be qualified to kneel before Yan Qingshu.

241
00:13:58,680 --> 00:14:00,880
Yan Qingshu, Yan Qingshu, Yan Qingshu.

242
00:14:01,400 --> 00:14:02,930
It's all about Yan Qingshu.

243
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:31,770
How could I be poisoned?

244
00:14:32,160 --> 00:14:34,040
It has already seeped into my bones,

245
00:14:34,040 --> 00:14:35,440
and I didn't even notice.

246
00:14:49,280 --> 00:14:50,320
Yan Mingli.

247
00:14:51,960 --> 00:14:53,960
Do you want me dead that badly?

248
00:14:58,040 --> 00:14:59,200
Well, I won't.

249
00:15:25,120 --> 00:15:26,080
Cuimei.

250
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:28,600
Yong.

251
00:15:29,200 --> 00:15:29,520
Huachao.

252
00:15:29,520 --> 00:15:30,760
Weikun Huachao.

253
00:15:32,440 --> 00:15:33,760
Long Cong Biao Hao.

254
00:15:37,320 --> 00:15:37,920
Shuang.

255
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:38,520
Shuang.

256
00:15:38,520 --> 00:15:39,880
Ningzheng.

257
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:43,280
Hao Chun Kang Shuai Hua.

258
00:15:46,680 --> 00:15:47,160
Wei Chao.

259
00:15:47,160 --> 00:15:47,690
Weichao.

260
00:15:49,160 --> 00:15:50,640
Qiang Yuan Liang Bo.

261
00:16:05,760 --> 00:16:06,120
Xi.

262
00:16:07,080 --> 00:16:07,400
Xi.

263
00:16:07,640 --> 00:16:07,760
Xi.

264
00:16:07,720 --> 00:16:08,080
Xi.

265
00:16:08,120 --> 00:16:09,240
Taoqiang.

266
00:16:12,840 --> 00:16:14,320
Hui Yue Yun Qing.

267
00:16:17,600 --> 00:16:18,520
Yiyi.

268
00:16:18,520 --> 00:16:18,850
Yi Yi.

269
00:16:25,560 --> 00:16:26,040
Si Si.
